Fix the bug. The label's enableShadow has wrong offset direction:

```typescript
const label = cc.Label.createWithSystemFont('Shadow', 'Arial', 24);
label.enableShadow(cc.color(0, 0, 0, 128), cc.size(5, 5), 0);
